Comment: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:26.59,ED Eng L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}These days you love me no more
Comment: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:33.23,ED Eng L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}nor am I still treasured by you
Comment: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:42.03,ED Eng L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Now I am all alone
Comment: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:49.91,ED Eng L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}What did you tell me when we parted?
Comment: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:56.54,ED Eng L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}The words hung in midair and never reached me
Comment: 0,0:21:57.00,0:22:03.30,ED Eng L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I know my dreams and wishes are illusory
Comment: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:09.93,ED Eng L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}and yet I cannot give up on them
Comment: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:19.94,ED Eng L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}You said, "Don't let go, hold onto my hand"
Comment: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:26.95,ED Eng L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}and, "We will always be together"
Comment: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:35.70,ED Eng L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Your hands as I held them were warm
Comment: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:44.00,ED Eng L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,2000)}and tender
Comment: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:26.59,ED Roma L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Mou anata kara aisareru koto mo
Comment: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:33.23,ED Roma L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}hitsuyou to sareru koto mo nai
Comment: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:42.03,ED Roma L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Soshite watashi wa koushite hitoribocchi de
Comment: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:49.91,ED Roma L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Ano toki anata wa nante itta no
Comment: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:56.54,ED Roma L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Todokanai kotoba wa chuu wo mau
Comment: 0,0:21:57.00,0:22:03.30,ED Roma L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Wakatteru no ni kyou mo shite shimau
Comment: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:09.93,ED Roma L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}kanawanu negaigoto wo
Comment: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:19.94,ED Roma L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Hanasanaide gyutto te wo nigittete
Comment: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:26.95,ED Roma L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}anata to futari tsudzuku to itte
Comment: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:35.70,ED Roma L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Tsunaida sono te wa atatakakute
