Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.01,0:01:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,975)}Você garantiu a chave?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.76,0:01:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,975)}Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.60,0:01:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,975)}Bom trabalho. Eu vou te guiar para fora.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.14,0:01:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,975)}Nos encontraremos em trinta segundos.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.18,0:02:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,975)}Por favor, Fyu-Neru, leve isso para Gai.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.37,0:03:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,975)}Eu te dou cobertura.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.37,0:03:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,975)}Agora leva isso para Gai, rápido!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.66,0:03:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,975)}Fyu-Neru...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.92,0:03:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,975)}Putz!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.89,0:04:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bom dia, Shu!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Para que o bocejo gigante?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.93,0:04:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.89,0:04:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Você estava navegando na rede ou algo do tipo?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.35,0:04:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ou jogando algum jogo?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.11,0:04:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Lendo?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.57,0:04:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Algo assim, eu suponho...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.15,0:04:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Certo, então.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.83,0:04:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Muita gente por aí hoje, hein?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Você não viu as notícias?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.71,0:04:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Aparentemente houve algum ataque terrorista ou algo assim ontem.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.96,0:04:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Em Odaiba... não, acho que agora é chamado de "Ala 24".
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.43,0:04:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei, Shu!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.27,0:04:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, desculpa, eu ainda não terminei aquele vídeo para a competição.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu não vim para te atormentar com isso...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,O que você queria, então?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.53,0:05:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu vou terminar até o prazo, não se preocupe.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.28,0:05:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Olha só, Shu, eu—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.61,0:05:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Deixa pra lá, Souta.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele diz que consegue fazer, afinal de contas.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.41,0:05:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Contamos com você!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinto muito por Souta.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.79,0:05:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Por quê? Acho que estou me esforçando para ser socialmente perceptivo aqui.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.46,0:05:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Você não está conseguindo.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.34,0:05:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Você é muito bobo demais.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.46,0:05:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ergue-se!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.05,0:05:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eu sou bobo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Talvez seja verdade que minha mente funciona fora de sincronia com a de todos os outros.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.68,0:05:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}É só que eu não sei o que dizer para as outras pessoas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.69,0:05:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Então eu escondo meu nervosismo e concordo com o que eles dizem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.94,0:05:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}é assim que fiz as quase amizades da minha vida.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.11,0:05:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}no momento, o Japão opera como uma nação "quase independente".{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.16,0:05:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}é o que minha mãe diz.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.45,0:05:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}há dez anos, a pandemia do Vírus do Apocalipse causou estragos neste país,{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.63,0:06:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}e dependemos de uma quantidade inacreditável de ajuda de muitos outros países.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.34,0:06:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}e ainda dependemos deles até hoje.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.55,0:06:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}os alicerces do Japão mal estão se mantendo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nós ouvimos isso todos os dias...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.35,0:06:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Nós não podemos deixar isso para você.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.35,0:06:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Você não tem o poder de proteger as pessoas que são importantes para você.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.24,0:06:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mas... devemos realmente aceitar isso?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.03,0:06:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Não há algo mais que eu possa fazer?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.46,0:06:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flor selvagem em flor...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.68,0:07:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eu imploro, por favor, me diga,{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.98,0:07:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Por que as pessoas lutam e machucam umas às outras?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.58,0:07:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flor em plena floração valente...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.51,0:07:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Quê—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Não, você entendeu errado!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.01,0:07:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu não queria de jeito nenhum...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.81,0:07:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei, você é...?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.12,0:07:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso... ainda não acabou!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.78,0:07:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,É uma vista da minha cidade natal, e...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.29,0:07:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,É bonito.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.62,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.63,0:08:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, você gostaria de um bolinho de arroz?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.43,0:08:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A Ponte de Londres está caindo, caindo, caindo.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.89,0:08:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A Ponte de Londres está caindo, minha bela dama.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.98,0:08:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, você é a Inori, não é?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.48,0:08:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A cantora Egoísta?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.24,0:08:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Ponte de Londres está caindo, caindo, caindo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.03,0:08:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Então, o que você está fazendo aqui?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Não, mais importante, por que você está tão ferido?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.95,0:08:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Temos que entregar isso para o Gai.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.46,0:08:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Pegue isto.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.79,0:08:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pegue isto, humm...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.42,0:08:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shu! Ouma Shu!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Você talvez consiga fazer se tentar.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.51,0:09:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas você nunca conseguirá sem tentar.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.10,0:09:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouma Shu... você é um covarde?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.44,0:09:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,O que foi aquilo?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.29,0:09:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fyu-Neru.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.58,0:09:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Inori!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.67,0:09:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei, espera aí.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.80,0:09:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Você é um estudante?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.09,0:09:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.51,0:09:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, aquela garota está ferida. Por favor, não a trate—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.72,0:09:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Esta mulher é uma criminosa.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.98,0:09:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Se você a defender, nós o purgaremos também, como cúmplice dela.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.40,0:09:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,O que a verificação de dados mostra?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.61,0:09:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ela é definitivamente membro do Sepolcro em Roppongi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.03,0:10:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Seu verme terrorista!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.41,0:10:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tragam-na.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.58,0:10:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.47,0:10:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu realmente devo aceitar isso?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu realmente devo aceitar isso?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.36,0:10:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eu me senti... um pouco aliviado, porque não estava mais em perigo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.79,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eu sou tão patético.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.58,0:10:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Quando se fala em verdade, ela estava fora da minha liga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.33,0:10:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pegue isto.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.25,0:10:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eu queria pegar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.38,0:11:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eu queria chegar perto dela e tocar a mão dela!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.10,0:11:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Esquece isso, Shu. Descanse um pouco, e você vai ficar bem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.56,0:11:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Depois disso, apenas volte a ser você mesmo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Temos que entregar isso para o Gai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.24,0:11:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sério? Você está me mandando ir até lá?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.76,0:11:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Esta pode ser minha última chance de não odiar a mim mesmo.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.85,0:11:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tinha que estar aqui, de todos os lugares...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.57,0:12:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Disseram-me que você despachou um esquadrão para Roppongi.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.62,0:12:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu acreditei que fosse necessário.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso vai provocar hostilidade desnecessária.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.91,0:12:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Não posso permitir isso se não for para uma missão de ajuda.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.96,0:12:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu entendo isso.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.63,0:12:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Então, quão perigoso é este Genoma Void roubado?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.51,0:12:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.26,0:12:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Informação classificada Nível 3A.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.22,0:12:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,E então você não pode nem me dizer isso, Comandante Supremo do GHQ?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Receio que sim, senhor.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.27,0:12:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas por favor, não se preocupe.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.02,0:12:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Meus Anti-Corpos já prenderam o culpado.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.78,0:12:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,e estamos procurando o genoma roubado neste momento.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.83,0:12:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ainda não quer falar?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.50,0:12:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nos foi concedida a autoridade de eliminar os doentes sem aviso prévio.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.63,0:13:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Se você não nos disser onde escondeu,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.76,0:13:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,eu terei que purgar cada residente deste bairro.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Você vai se arrepender disso depois.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Atenção, todas as unidades.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.90,0:13:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Todos os residentes em nossa área de operação foram designados como infectados Estágio IV+.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.19,0:13:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Autorizo as medidas de controle de infecção!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.78,0:13:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,O que vamos fazer com a garota?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.08,0:13:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Depois que começarmos as hostilidades, livre-se dela lá fora.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.72,0:13:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,É só isso?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.97,0:13:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei, você!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sim?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.23,0:13:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso já tá pronto?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Desculpe?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Esse objeto cozinha arroz?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.94,0:14:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem, não, eu não {\i1}acho{\i0} que sim...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.41,0:14:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Deixa isso.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.53,0:14:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Não, eu não posso fazer isso!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.45,0:14:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Você tá brincando comigo? Apenas entregue isso.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.46,0:14:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Me desculpe, mas isso não é meu!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.50,0:14:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ela trabalhou tanto para proteger isto...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.88,0:14:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Então... Me desculpe!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.77,0:14:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Saudações, meus caros falecidos.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.02,0:14:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Falecidos"?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.53,0:14:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim. A situação atual não permite a sua sobrevivência.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.62,0:14:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Portanto, vocês estão todos mortos.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Não diga que ele é...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.96,0:14:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...Gai!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.91,0:15:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Você tem coragem, garoto.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.26,0:15:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Caramba, quem é esse cara?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.66,0:15:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê...?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.50,0:15:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,É a Fyu-Neru, certo? Devolve!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.72,0:15:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Você é o Ouma Shu?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.14,0:16:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,E a garota que estava com ele/isso?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.27,0:16:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem... eu...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.65,0:16:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Você acabou de abandoná-la?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.37,0:16:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Gai! Os uniformizados brancos do GHQ estão invadindo!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.59,0:16:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Malditos bastardos! Eles estão disparando balas reais em qualquer um que virem!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.97,0:16:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi, qual a situação de Ayase e dos outros?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.10,0:16:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles estão...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.27,0:16:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Inimigo chegando pela nossa esquerda!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai da frente, você tá no meu caminho!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Vai, Shu!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.16,0:17:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Não ouse largar aquilo! Protege ele desta vez!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.26,0:17:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Mas... o que eu posso fazer, exatamente?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.43,0:17:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Com quantos nós estamos enfrentando?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.19,0:17:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ainda não sei! Mais coisas estão chegando!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mantenha a calma!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,O que você pensa que está fazendo?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Inori!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.82,0:18:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Faça algo que não seja típico de você, Shu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.98,0:18:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê...?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.20,0:18:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.41,0:19:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shu, por favor...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.66,0:19:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...use-me.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.33,0:19:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Desta vez, aceite isso, Shu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.96,0:19:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Quem...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.13,0:19:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Este é poder.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.76,0:19:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A coroa culpada que ganha forma através do laço entre os corações.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.46,0:20:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,O que... é isto?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.75,0:21:26.76,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Hoje em dia, você não me ama mais
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.39,0:21:33.39,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}nem eu sou mais valorizado por você
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.77,0:21:42.19,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Agora estou completamente sozinho
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.99,0:21:50.08,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}O que você me disse quando nos despedimos?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.70,0:21:56.71,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}As palavras ficaram suspensas no ar e nunca chegaram até mim
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.17,0:22:03.46,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Eu sei que meus sonhos e desejos são ilusórios
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.05,0:22:10.10,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}e ainda assim não consigo desistir deles
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.14,0:22:20.11,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Você disse: "Não solte, segure minha mão
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.65,0:22:27.11,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}E, 'nós sempre estaremos juntos
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.28,0:22:35.87,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Suas mãos, quando eu as segurei, estavam quentes
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.00,0:22:44.17,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,2000)}e terno
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.75,0:21:26.76,ED Roma L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Mou anata kara aisareru koto mo
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.39,0:21:33.39,ED Roma L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}nem ser necessário.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.77,0:21:42.19,ED Roma L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}E assim eu estou aqui, completamente sozinha(o).
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.99,0:21:50.08,ED Roma L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Ano toki anata wa nante itta no?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.70,0:21:56.71,ED Roma L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}As palavras que não chegam flutuam no ar.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.17,0:22:03.46,ED Roma L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Apesar de saber, ainda acabo fazendo hoje.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.05,0:22:10.10,ED Roma L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Kanawanu negaigoto wo
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.14,0:22:20.11,ED Roma L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Sem se ajoelhar, você segura minhas mãos com força
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.65,0:22:27.11,ED Roma L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Anata to futari tsuzuku to itte
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.28,0:22:35.87,ED Roma L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Tsunaida sono te wa atatakakute yasashikatta
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.00,0:22:44.17,ED Roma L1,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,2000)}Foi gentil
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:32.63,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(5080,5130,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Flor que desabrocha no campo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:40.01,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(2536,2586,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(4538,4588,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(6832,6882,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Ah, por favor, me diga
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:56.32,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(4413,4463,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(8542,8592,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(11628,11678,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Por que as pessoas se machucam e lutam umas contra as outras?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:01:04.46,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(659,709,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(3788,3838,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Flor desabrochando bravamente
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:11.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(3287,3337,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}O que você pode ver do seu campo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:28.52,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(4664,4714,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(9627,9677,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(12588,12638,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(15424,15474,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Por que as pessoas não conseguem perdoar umas às outras?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:40.37,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(2536,2586,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(4538,4588,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(7040,7090,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}A chuva passou, e o verão ganhou tons azuis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:47.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(1118,1168,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(3495,3545,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(6165,6215,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Sozinho agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:56.42,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(1952,2002,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(5497,5547,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Você tremeu na minha frente.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:02:04.43,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(1702,1752,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(3579,3629,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(6039,6089,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Sem dizer uma única palavra
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:27.58,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(1994,2044,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(3745,3795,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(5747,5797,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Quando seus amigos murcham ao seu redor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:35.67,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(1.25,\3c&H000000&)}O que você acha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:43.81,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(450,500,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(2953,3003,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(6415,6465,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Com essas folhas que não possuem palavras
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:52.27,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(1076,1126,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(3537,3587,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(5498,5548,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(6081,6131,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(6550,8425,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Como você transmite o amor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:03:04.66,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(3579,3629,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(6540,6590,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(7541,7591,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}O sol de verão está nublado, e o vento passa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:12.00,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(825,875,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(3286,3336,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Os dois se sobrepuseram
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:20.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(10,1885,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(2035,2085,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(3745,3795,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(5205,5255,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(6874,6924,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Eu cantarei a prova de que você viveu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:31.98,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(451,501,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(502,1127,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(1160,1210,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(1211,1544,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(1744,1794,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(1795,3129,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(4747,4797,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(7958,8008,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Pelo bem daqueles que não têm nomes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:32.63,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(5080,5130,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Saita no no hana yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:40.01,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(2536,2586,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(4538,4588,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(6832,6882,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Aa douka oshiete okure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:56.32,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(4413,4463,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(8542,8592,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(11628,11678,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Hito wa naze kizutsukeatte arasou no deshou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:01:04.46,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(659,709,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(3788,3838,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Rin to saku hana no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:11.84,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(3287,3337,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Soko kara nani ga mieru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:28.52,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(4664,4714,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(9627,9677,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(12588,12638,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(15424,15474,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Hito wa naze yurushiau koto dekinai no deshou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:40.37,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(2536,2586,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(4538,4588,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(7040,7090,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Ame wa agari natsu wa aoku utsuru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:47.71,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(1118,1168,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(3495,3545,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(6165,6215,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Hitotsu ni natte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:56.42,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(1952,2002,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(5497,5547,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Na minha frente, quem tremeu levemente.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:02:04.43,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(1702,1752,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(3579,3629,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(6039,6089,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Sem dizer nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:27.58,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(1994,2044,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(3745,3795,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(5747,5797,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Com o passar do tempo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:35.67,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(1.25,\3c&H000000&)}O que você está pensando?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:43.81,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(450,500,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(2953,3003,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(6415,6465,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Como aquela folha sem palavras
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:52.27,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\t(1076,1126,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(3537,3587,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(5498,5548,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(6081,6131,1.5,\3c&H000000&)\t(6550,8425,1.5,\3c&H000000&)}Transmitindo o amor
